 * pseudocode
 *
 * Backtracking(state)
 * 		if invalid(state)	//e.g. we reached a # or the location is already visited
 * 			return
 *
 * 		if found_solution(state)
 * 			mark_solution_found
 * 			return
 *
 * 		for each child_state of state
 * 			state' = do changes in state
 *
 * 			Backtracking(state')
 *
 * 			state = undo changes in state'
 *https://github.com/mostafa-saad/ArabicCompetitiveProgramming/blob/master/10%20Search%20Techniques/Algorithms_Search_Techniques_03_Backtracking.cpp
